{"TopicId":174750,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"Unlocked actiongroups","CreatedByName":"xanos","CreatedById":33225,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-08T17:51:26Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"xanos","CreatedById":33225,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-08T17:51:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have been looking around, and is there a mod that unlock actiongroups from the start?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI plan to run a IVA only campaign. After launching, I don\u0027t want to see the outside of the craft at all unless I EVA. But I need to be able to run experiments and deploy stuff.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyone have any tips?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-08T18:17:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s actually in the difficulty settings, under the Advanced tab.\u00A0 \u0022Always allow action groups\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"xanos","CreatedById":33225,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-05-08T18:58:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223374041\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022174750\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221525803468\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n40 minutes ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s actually in the difficulty settings, under the Advanced tab.\u00A0 \u0022Always allow action groups\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHuh! So it is!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI completely missed that, thank you. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}